# Mobile Design System Rules

## Color tokens — always use semantic tokens, never hardcoded values

```tsx
// ✅ correct
<Text className="text-foreground" />
<View className="bg-primary" />
<View className="bg-background" />

// ❌ wrong — never hardcode
<Text style={{ color: '#2b5b7e' }} />
<View style={{ backgroundColor: '#1a5c4b' }} />
<View className="bg-[#f5f0e8]" />
```

### Token reference
| Token | Color | Use for |
|---|---|---|
| `bg-background` | cream #f5f0e8 | Screen backgrounds |
| `bg-card` | white #ffffff | Card surfaces |
| `bg-primary` | teal #1a5c4b | Primary actions, CTAs |
| `text-foreground` | deep blue #2b5b7e | Body text |
| `text-muted-foreground` | slate #5b7d99 | Secondary/helper text |
| `text-primary-foreground` | white | Text on teal bg |
| `bg-secondary` | warm off-white #faf7f2 | Section backgrounds |
| `bg-accent` | light teal #eaf3ef | Icon backgrounds, highlights |
| `border-border` | light navy #dce3ea | Borders, dividers |
| `bg-destructive` | red #b91c1c | Errors, destructive actions |

## Component primitives — always use Gluestack, not raw React Native

```tsx
// ✅ correct
import { View } from '@/components/ui/view';
import { Text } from '@/components/ui/text';
import { HStack } from '@/components/ui/hstack';
import { VStack } from '@/components/ui/vstack';
import { Card } from '@/components/ui/card';
import { SafeAreaView } from '@/components/ui/safe-area-view';
import { ScrollView } from '@/components/ui/scroll-view';

// ❌ wrong
import { View, Text, ScrollView } from 'react-native';
```

## Border radius — match web exactly

| Component | Class |
|---|---|
| Button | `rounded-[10px]` (already set in component) |
| Input | `rounded-[10px]` (already set in component) |
| Card | `rounded-xl` |
| Badge | `rounded-[6px]` (already set in component) |
| Avatar | `rounded-full` |
| Feature icon bg | `rounded-xl` |

## Typography — always DM Sans

```tsx
// ✅ correct — font-sans resolves to DM Sans
<Text className="font-sans text-base font-medium text-foreground" />
<Text className="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground" />  // DM Mono for code

// ❌ wrong — never rely on platform default font
<Text style={{ fontFamily: 'System' }} />
<Text />  // no font class = platform default
```

Font weights available: `font-normal` (400), `font-medium` (500), `font-semibold` (600), `font-bold` / `font-black` (700).

## Shadows — use named tokens

```tsx
<Card className="shadow-sm" />   // subtle card lift
<Card className="shadow-md" />   // elevated card
<Card className="shadow-lg" />   // modal/sheet
```

Never use `style={{ shadowColor: ... }}` directly — the tokens use navy-tinted rgba values matching the web.
